1080
01:00:05.122 --> 01:00:05.132
Mm.

1081
01:00:05.142 --> 01:00:07.242
In it being able to explain exactly what was going on.

1082
01:00:07.402 --> 01:00:07.722
Yeah.

1083
01:00:08.042 --> 01:00:11.762
